## Architectural Rules

* Display owns rendering only
* Intelligence owns reasoning only
* State owns runtime state only
* Controller owns orchestration only
* Autonomy (Stage 200) is read-only

---

## System Definition

This system is a structured, layered architecture designed for:

* stability
* scaling
* fault isolation
* controlled autonomy
* continuous runtime execution

The system operates as a closed-loop runtime engine with strict separation of concerns across all layers.


